Package: moultR
Title: Summarise and Plot Bird Moult Card Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Fer", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "farcego@gmail.com")
Description: Tools to organise, summarise, analyse and plot bird moult
    card data. The package includes schematic wing diagrams for visualising
    feather moult extent and functions to prepare moult card records for
    further analysis.
